{
  "stem": "27507.11",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were told maybe it was not-- maybe it didn't happen-- that there was very likely possibility that the gestapo found in this place a paper with names and addresses of the members of the organization.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And if that happened, then we were gone and finished.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And Goldstein said then enough is enough, I am not stay here anymore.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we didn't leave because there was nowhere to leave.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And stayed only in the flat, and somehow the gestapo never appeared.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we were extremely lucky.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Maybe they never found the paper.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "On another occasion, there was-- they surrounded all of the area, and were-- got all of the people out and were making searches and selection.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Those things happened in Polish area, as well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And were searching the houses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we were all sitting on this occasion in the cellar and really not having much hope that we'll survive this time.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And what happened, what was worse, was that there was this cellar.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There was a hole to the outside, which appeared on the outside as a hole.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was kind of a long hole so that you couldn't look into the cellar, but there was a hole near the ground level.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And because it was-- and because the Germans were around, I think my father pushed some rags or clothes into that hole so that if there was any sound, that they wouldn't hear from outside.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then the Germans were walking outside, and we heard them that they found those rags and they got their rags out.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were talking to one another, what does it mean, and where are those regs from?",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
